IN ORDER TO START THE SERVER WITH THE WEBSITE FOLLOW THESE STEPS
-----------------------------------------------------------------
1. INSTALL FOLLOWING NPM PACKAGES:
npm i, 
npm i express,
npm i ejs, 
npm i axios

2. Run the server using : nodemon index.js, in order to start the website


